Package dijkstra

Class PreviousFunction

java.lang.Object
dijkstra.PreviousFunction
All Implemented Interfaces:
Previous
public class PreviousFunction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Previous
This class implements a function from the set of the visited vertices to itself. For each visited vertex, it returns its parent in the tree built by the algorithm.
